display_long_description:
Become the ultimate food thief in Hungry Cat!
Slip into the life of a mischievous stray cat in full immersive VR. Sneak into houses, dodge humans, and snatch tasty meals while exploring every corner of a cozy home. Use your paws to open cabinets, knock objects off shelves, and pounce on your favorite snacks with realistic room-scale movement that makes you feel truly inside the world.
Every mission brings new challenges; from grabbing fish off the counter to raiding the fridge without getting caught. The detailed environments and playful physics make each moment unpredictable, hilarious, and full of feline mischief. Whether you’re climbing, jumping, or stealing, the freedom of interactive VR gameplay gives you the perfect mix of chaos and charm.
Designed for Meta Quest players, Hungry Cat combines exploration, stealth, and fun into one unforgettable virtual reality adventure. Get ready to test your skills, sharpen your instincts, and feed your hunger; one stolen snack at a time!
